short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Changes tent city or detention center to Concentration Camp on website

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This application does one simple thing.  It autocorrects the phrases "tent city" and "detention center" to what they really are, Concentration Camps.
